### Reset All Data - Delete all members, sessions, polls from DB and photos from Cloudinary
### Update the host below to match your environment (localhost or Render URL)

@host = https://vanigan-id-card.onrender.com
@adminKey = change-this-admin-key

### -------------------------------------------------------
### 1. Reset ALL data (members + sessions + polls + cloudinary photos)
### -------------------------------------------------------
DELETE {{host}}/api/v1/admin/reset-all
X-Admin-Key: {{adminKey}}

### -------------------------------------------------------
### 2. Delete a SINGLE member by unique_id (also removes photo from Cloudinary)
###    Replace TVSM000000000 with the actual unique_id
### -------------------------------------------------------
DELETE {{host}}/api/v1/admin/members/TVSM000000000
X-Admin-Key: {{adminKey}}

### -------------------------------------------------------
### 3. List all members (to find unique_ids)
### -------------------------------------------------------
GET {{host}}/api/v1/admin/members
X-Admin-Key: {{adminKey}}
